           <h1 class="responsive-headline">Miguel Beneitez</h1>
           <h3>I am a PhD student in Fluid Mechanics at
	     KTH Royal Institute of Technology.
	     My research focuses on subcritical transition of shear flows using tools from dynamical systems and large-scale simulations.
       We hope to better understand the transition from laminar to turbulent flow in our work.
             <!-- Let's <a class="smoothscroll" href="#about">start scrolling</a>
             and learn more <a class="smoothscroll" href="#about">about me</a>.--> </h3>
            <hr />
