           <h2>About Me</h2>

            <p>I was born in Madrid, Spain where I studied Mechanical Engineering with an specialization in Energy Technologies. Afterwards I moved to Stockholm to further specialise in Fluid Mechanics and now I am doing my PhD under the supervision of <a href=https://www.mech.kth.se/~henning/ target=_blank>Prof. Dan Henningson</a>, <a href=https://www.mech.kth.se/mech/info_staff.jsp?ID=216 target=_blank>Prof. Philipp Schlatter</a> and <a href=https://perso.limsi.fr/duguet/ target=_blank>Yohann Duguet</a>.
            </p>

	    <h2>Short CV</h2>
