                  <p>
                    I am also enthusiastic about science communication and reading about
		    math and physics in general. It is always great checking <a href=https://www.quantamagazine.org/>Quanta Magazine</a> and <a href=https://fuckyeahfluiddynamics.tumblr.com/>FYFD</a> among others. Additionally, I am interested in open-source software and in the <a href=https://julialang.org/> Julia</a> programming language.
                  </p>

                  <p>
                    During the covid-19 crisis I tried to introduce Chaos theory for kids
		    who could not go to school due to the lockdown in many countries in a lesson together with <a href=https://encounteredu.com/>Encounteredu</a>. The video is available <a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DqlVgovDX3Y>here!</a>
